--- SorceryNet Nickname Services Help ---
 
 === VACATION ===
 
     SYNTAX:
     /NickServ VACATION
 
     DESCRIPTION:
     The NickServ VACATION command provides a way to increase the
     expiration time in NickServ for your current nickname from 25
     days to 75 days.  This command is only available if your nick
     has been registered for at least 25 days.  Vacation mode is disabled
     the next time you come online.
 
     NOTE: VACATION will not effect the expiration time period
     for channels founded using your nickname.

     EXAMPLES:
     To set your current nick on vacation:
       /NickServ vacation
 
